Cast
====

Syntax:
  cast <spellname> [at <target>]

Casts a Rifts spell using PPE (Potential Psychic Energy). You must know the
spell and have enough PPE to pay its cost.

Examples:
  cast fire bolt at brodkil
  cast armor of ithan
  cast cloud of smoke

In combat, casting uses one attack per melee (APM) for that round.

Type help spells for the Rifts L1-L5 spell list. Which spells you know
depends on your O.C.C.

See also: help spells, score, rest
